headline: Accenture to Announce First-Quarter Fiscal 2026 Results
summary: NEW YORK, December 02, 2025--Accenture will host a conference call at 8:00 a.m. EST on Thursday, December 18, 2025, to discuss its first-quarter fiscal 2026 financial results.
